{"tid":544591,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"舊居遺留的舊黑膠/LD","createTime":"2018-01-29T16:13:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-29T16:30:12.000Z","uid":5218,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d1c89219c176ebffa22b75568db49460979bb791","tid":544591,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T16:13:06.000Z","msg":"前幾天返媽媽屋企食飯，佢同我講話有堆舊黑膠問我擺左咁耐仲要唔要，先發覺原來我仲有野向舊屋度。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n下面幾隻分別有小島樂隊，白花油王子既川鳴樂隊、鄭敬基既風雲樂隊同九十年代頭既新人劉祖兒。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/30/000147_d8e29df1a856902ae04b76d8baa0f17a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F30%2F000147_d8e29df1a856902ae04b76d8baa0f17a.png&h=8343e5b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/30/000151_ebb92cb1d22f21d73d2b46bc0e63025c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F30%2F000151_ebb92cb1d22f21d73d2b46bc0e63025c.png&h=d63ed4fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/30/000208_7a09b12c2dffb7910106bb8f6b67845f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F30%2F000208_7a09b12c2dffb7910106bb8f6b67845f.png&h=faa7a4f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/30/000213_7bf15525e4f4f47364a213e4ad588100.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F30%2F000213_7bf15525e4f4f47364a213e4ad588100.png&h=ab308420&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7ae9ac207bc847e25ce19993fb26e1630a2abf89","tid":544591,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T16:14:44.000Z","msg":"跟著有幾隻達明同 beyond。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj